description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for highly motivated domestic assistant to provide a high quality domestic service to the Health Centre, working either individually or as part of a team ensuring a clean and safe environment is maintained for patient staff and visitors.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Following agreed work schedules methods and procedures in accordance with the national standards of cleanliness.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post is based at Long Eaton Health centre. However, the post holder will be required to have a flexible approach and be prepared to work on other sites should service demands dictate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sue Kerry, IFM hotel Services Domestic Supervisor&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;sue.kerry1@nhs.net, 07973 979447&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jayne Elliott, 07598 97337, jayne .elliott1@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
